%h4 Most improved batting average( hits / at-bats) from 2009 to 2010 for the players with at least 200 at-bats.
- unless @most_improved_battings.blank?
  %table{class: "table table-striped table-bordered table-condensed"}
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Palyer Id
        %th Player Name
        %th Most Improved Batting AVG
    %tbody
      - @most_improved_battings.each do |batting|
        %tr
          %td= batting.player_id
          %td= batting.player.name rescue ''
          %td= batting.batting_average

